raw_text = "~ start
## 10pm
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Psst. You awake babe? 🥱
Player: For you? Always
Mabel: Hehe good answer 🥰
Mabel: I can't sleep
Player: Neighbor still making noise?
Mabel: No noise today!! 😄
Mabel: More like nervous about tomorrow
Mabel: But I don't wanna think about that right now
Mabel: I just wanna talk to you 🥺
- I'm all yours
	Player: I'm all yours
	Mabel: Eee. My favorite words 🥰
	Mabel: Maybe second actually 🤭 Hehehe
- What's on your mind Mabes?
	Player: What's on your mind Mabes?
	Mabel: Nothing's really on my mind
	Mabel: I just missed you
Mabel: Can I be a little sappy for a sec?
Player: Sure 😊
Mabel: I was just lying here thinking about us
Mabel: Like how did I get this lucky
Mabel: You've known me since I was still tripping on my shoelaces lol
Player: And the permanent runny nose 😃
Mabel: SO not cute, never bring that up again!! 😫
Mabel: PinkThought: Can't believe you stuck by my side the whole way through
Mabel: I just can't wait to spend some time with you
do heart(1)
Mabel: Like, whatever happens, I always come back to you
Mabel: That's the deal, right? 🥰
- That's the deal 🩷
	Player: That's the deal 🩷
	Mabel: 🥹🥹
- Always, Mabes
	Player: Always Mabes
	Mabel: 🥹
Mabel: Can we make it a promise?
Player: Of course!
Mabel: Pinky promise then 🤙
Player: 🤙
Mabel: 🥺🩷
Mabel: Thought: As long as I've got him, I can handle anything
Mabel: Okayyy enough sap before I soak my whole pillow 😭😂
Player: 😂😊
Mabel: Thought: ...
Mabel: Thought: Weird, the butterflies just won't settle
Mabel: PinkThought: M-maybe I should make a move
do heart(2)
Mabel: Babe?
Mabel: Are you.. uhm... you know
Mabel: C-curious of me?
Mabel: I mean... uhh what I'm trying to say is
Mabel: Did you ever wanna... exchange a few pictures sometimes?
Mabel: Since we're exclusive and all that... I don't know if I'm making any sense right now
- You mean like.. intimately?
	set Story.flag = \"SharePicMabel\"
	Player: You mean like.. intimately?
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Thought: Thank God he got it
	Mabel: PinkThought: We're on the same page hehe
	Mabel: Mmmh yeah 🫢 Like that
	Player: Yeah, if you're okay with it
	Mabel: I...
	Mabel: I think I see girls getting all intimate with their boyfriends
	Mabel: Thought: And sometimes NOT their boyfriends
	Mabel: Thought: How could anyone do that to their boyfriend...
	Mabel: So I kinda wanna.. uhm... try it with you 😶
	Mabel: If you don't mind...
	Player: I don't mind 😊
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: Well uhm...
	Mabel: Okay here goes nothing!
	Mabel: img: mabel/201
	Player: Wow... 😍
	Player: That's not your usual PJs though
	Mabel: Ehm... yeah... 😅
	Mabel: This is part of a Sorority assimilation thing apparently
	Mabel: \"All Sorority girls must be dressed like a true Sorority girl\"
	Mabel: Something silly like that 😆
	- Is it comfortable?
		Player: Is it comfortable?
		Mabel: Not really... I prefer my PJs
		do heart(1)
		Mabel: These are a bit tight
		Mabel: PinkThought: They also sorta squeeze my crotch area
		Mabel: But I guess I have to haha
	- Do you like wearing it?
		Player: Do you like wearing it?
		do heart(1)
		Mabel: It's a bit more... revealing than I'd like haha..
		Mabel: Yeah I don't really know how I'd feel if someone other than you were to see me like this 😅
		Mabel: PinkThought: I think... I look good like this
	Mabel: img: mabel/202
	Mabel: Do I look nice? 👉👈
	Player: Yeah
	Mabel: Awwh thanks babe 🥰
	Mabel: PinkThought: I wish you could lie down with you in person
- You mean like a selfie?
	Player: You mean like a selfie?
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Thought: Oh no... He didn't catch it..
	Mabel: Y'know what, nevermind 🥰
	Mabel: Thought: I'm a little too tired and nervous to explain it ugh
do heart(0)
Mabel: I really should sleep for tomorrow 🥹
Mabel: I'll be super brave, like a spy 🫡
Mabel: And I'll tell you ALL about it when I can 😊
Player: Would be fun!
Mabel: Night night, my favorite person 🩷
Player: Night Mabes. Love you
Mabel: My fav set of words hehe
Mabel: Love you more ☺️😴
=> END
"
